verse.lines:
There’ll be no sorrow there
When we get over yonder;
There’ll be no sorrow there
When we get over yonder;
There’ll be no sorrow there
When we get over yonder;
Ohhhhhh! Won’t we have a time?

We’ll crown him Lord of all
When we get over yonder;
We’ll crown him Lord of all
When we get over yonder;
We’ll crown him Lord of all
When we get over yonder;
Ohhhhhh! Won’t we have a time?
